sequenceDiagram
    %% --- Dual-Path Metadata Resolution for 'wl get' ---

    participant C as wl get (Client)
    participant T as Tracker API
    participant P as P2P Swarm

    C->>C: Parse magnet link (extract info_hash)
    
    Note over C, T: PATH 1: Fast Path (Weightless Tracker)
    C->>T: GET /api/registry/{info_hash}
    
    alt Found in Registry
        T-->>C: 200 OK (Full .torrent dict)
        C->>C: Parse metadata, initialize download
    else Not Found / Third-Party Tracker
        T-->>C: 404 / Connection Error
        
        Note over C, P: PATH 2: Standard Path (BEP 9 Metadata Exchange)
        C->>T: GET /announce?info_hash=...
        T-->>C: Peer List
        C->>P: TCP Connect & Handshake
        C->>P: BEP 10 Extension Handshake (ut_metadata)
        C->>P: Request Metadata Pieces
        P-->>C: Metadata Pieces
        C->>C: Assemble & Verify SHA-1 against info_hash
    end
    
    Note over C, P: DOWNLOADING PHASE
    C->>C: Pre-allocate file on disk
    C->>P: Request Data Pieces (BEP 3)
